  <section class="brand--department-for-business-innovation-skills brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--padding   govuk-!-margin-bottom-3">
  What we do
</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>Securing our long-term energy supply, bringing down bills and halving inflation.</p>

<p><abbr title="Department for Energy Security and Net Zero">DESNZ</abbr> is a ministerial department, supported by <a class="govuk-link" href="/government/organisations#department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero">14 agencies and public bodies</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero/about" class="govuk-link brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>    </div>

